{"title":"THE BLACK VAULT","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"certified-lover-ltd-ed","title":"CERTIFIED LOVER","description":"\r\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\r\nEmbroidery work front\/back.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM black oversized T-shirt is crafted to offer a bold, streetwear-inspired aesthetic with premium details. Designed with a white cloth lining running from top to bottom, as well as from the front neck to the shoulder area, it brings a fresh touch to your look. The front features an embroidered logo, adding a touch of sophistication and an elevated vibe to the piece. On the back, the embroidered “Certified Lover” (that too in embroidery) print adds an extra layer of exclusivity. Perfect for those who appreciate luxury and street style, this T-shirt combines comfort, durability, and high-end craftsmanship.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\r\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46881407434906,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881407467674,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881407500442,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881407533210,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881407598746,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46881407631514,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":1649.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00022copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440426"},{"product_id":"rules-breaker-black","title":"RULES BREAKER I - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Fabric. Oversized Fit with Raglan Sleeves. Front Embroidery \u0026amp; Back Silicone Print. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis oversized 240 GSM waffle T-shirt from Drip Studios is built for comfort with a refined edge. Designed with raglan sleeves for enhanced mobility and a relaxed drape, it delivers a super-comfy yet decent silhouette. The front features a clean embroidered “Rules Breaker” logo, keeping it minimal and premium, while the back makes a bold statement with a high-quality silicone print reading “Rules Breaker.” Crafted from combed and bio-washed cotton waffle fabric, this tee offers breathability, texture, and lasting softness—perfect for elevated everyday wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM waffle fabric for a textured, premium feel. Oversized fit for a relaxed and comfortable silhouette. Raglan sleeves for improved movement and fit. Front embroidered logo with back silicone print for durability and style. Unisex design suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408843930,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408876698,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408909466,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408942234,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46881408975002,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46881409007770,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00497copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440585"},{"product_id":"stand-alone-jersey","title":"STAND ALONE JERSEY","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM\r\n100% French Terry Cotton\r\nBoxy Fit\r\nV - Neck\r\n3-D High Density Print Front\/Back\r\nWhite Fabric Piping on arms and V neck\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nCombed and Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOversized Boxy Fit V-Neck Jersey T-Shirt – \"Fear No One \/ Against All Odds\"\r\n\r\nStep into bold confidence with our oversized boxy fit V-neck jersey T-shirt, crafted from premium cotton for all-day comfort and effortless streetwear appeal. This relaxed silhouette features a front high-density print that reads \"FEAR NO ONE\", delivering a strong statement with a clean, elevated texture. On the back, the power continues with a matching high-density \"AGAINST ALL ODDS\" graphic—because your style should speak just as loud as your mindset.\r\n\r\n100% 260 GSM cotton for breathable comfort\r\n\r\nOversized, boxy fit with dropped shoulders for a modern streetwear look\r\n\r\nV-neckline for a relaxed yet refined edge\r\n\r\nHigh-density front and back prints for a bold, textured finish\r\n\r\nStatement graphics: \"FEAR NO ONE\" (front) \/ \"AGAINST ALL ODDS\" (back)\r\n\r\nWear it with confidence. Stand for something.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"L","offer_id":46885164712090,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885164744858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885164777626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"S","offer_id":46885164843162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885164875930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885164908698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00177copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440486"},{"product_id":"black-polo","title":"BLACK POLO","description":"\u003cp\u003e220 GSM. Super Premium Matte Lycra Fabric. Refined Polo Construction. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Gender-Neutral. Tailored Regular Fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis super-premium 220 GSM polo T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for those who appreciate quiet luxury in everyday essentials. Crafted from a refined matte lycra blend, the fabric offers a smooth, elevated finish with natural stretch for comfort and structure. The tailored regular fit delivers a sharp, composed silhouette, while the classic polo collar adds a touch of timeless sophistication.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCombed and bio-washed for exceptional softness and durability, this polo balances breathability, polish, and long-lasting performance. Built to transition seamlessly from relaxed settings to elevated occasions, it stands as a modern wardrobe staple defined by restraint, precision, and premium craftsmanship.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWash inside out with similar colors using cold water to preserve the fabric’s finish and depth. Avoid harsh detergents. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain shape and elasticity. Store folded in a cool, dry space to retain its premium quality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM super-premium matte lycra fabric for a smooth, luxurious finish. Refined polo collar for timeless versatility. Tailored regular fit for a composed, elevated silhouette. Combed cotton blend ensures breathability and all-day comfort. Bio-washed treatment enhances softness, durability, and fabric longevity.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064528289946,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064528322714,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064528355482,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064528421018,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00068copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440229"},{"product_id":"raglan-cropped-tee-black","title":"RAGLAN CROPPED TEE - BLACK","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium French Terry Cotton. Cropped Silhouette with Raglan Full Sleeves. Minimal Design. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cropped 240 GSM full-sleeve T-shirt from Drip Studios is crafted for a clean, super-decent everyday look. Designed with raglan sleeves, it offers a relaxed shoulder fit and effortless movement, while the cropped length adds a modern, balanced silhouette. Made from premium French terry cotton, this tee delivers softness, breathability, and lasting comfort. With its basic, minimal aesthetic and refined finish, it’s a versatile essential that pairs easily with any wardrobe for understated style.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to preserve fabric quality. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to maintain the fabric’s integrity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM French terry fabric for a lightweight yet premium feel. Cropped length with full raglan sleeves for a relaxed, modern fit. Gender-neutral design suitable for diverse body types. Soft, breathable combed cotton for all-day comfort. Bio-washed finish ensures durability and a smooth hand feel.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064597168282,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-C