helps keep you dry during any athletic activity. True to size—recommended to order your usual size.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064627019930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064627052698,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064627085466,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064627118234,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00715copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440796"},{"product_id":"black-dry-fit-vest","title":"BLACK DRY-FIT VEST","description":"\u003cp\u003eLightweight Fabric. Slim Fit. Sleeveless Vest. 100% Recycled Polyester. Dry Fit Performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis slim-fit Dry Fit vest is designed for comfort and performance across all athletic activities. Crafted from lightweight recycled polyester, it feels soft against the skin while allowing maximum airflow and unrestricted movement. The moisture-wicking Dry Fit fabric helps keep you dry and comfortable during workouts, training sessions, and active routines. Finished with a clean, minimal silhouette, this vest delivers a sleek athletic look while supporting high-performance wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash with similar colors in cold water. Avoid fabric softeners to maintain moisture-wicking performance. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLightweight recycled polyester fabric for breathability and comfort. Slim fit for a close-to-body, performance-ready feel. Sleeveless design for enhanced airflow and freedom of movement. Dry Fit technology helps manage moisture during any athletic activity. True to size—recommended to order your usual size.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47064627839130,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47064627871898,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47064627904666,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47064627937434,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00748copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440848"},{"product_id":"henley-black","title":"HENLEY - BLACK","description":"\u003cp\u003eMODEL HEIGHT 5'9\" WEARING M SIZE\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM. Hefty Cotton Fabric. Slim Fit Body-Hugging Silhouette. 96% Cotton \u0026amp; 4% Spandex. Gender-Neutral. Made in India.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 220 GSM slim-fit T-shirt is designed to elevate everyday essentials with a refined, body-hugging silhouette. Crafted from a luxurious blend of 96% cotton and 4% spandex, it offers the perfect balance of softness, stretch, and structure for all-day comfort. The hefty cotton fabric delivers a smooth, premium hand feel while maintaining breathability and shape retention. Thoughtfully made in India, this tee is built to move with you—enhancing your style with clean lines, superior fit, and lasting quality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Do not bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric stretch and shape. Iron on low heat if required. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e220 GSM hefty cotton fabric for a premium, structured feel. Slim-fit, body-hugging design that enhances natural shape. 96% cotton and 4% spandex blend for softness, flexibility, and comfort. Breathable construction suitable for everyday wear. Excellent stretch and recovery for long-term shape retention. Made in India with a focus on quality craftsmanship.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47079282835610,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":47079282868378,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":47079282901146,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47079282933914,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1499.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00065copy_11zon.jpg?v=1771440076"},{"product_id":"regular-cropped-tee-black-copy","title":"REGULAR CROPPED TEE - BLACK","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Relaxed Waist. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios is designed for effortless everyday wear. Crafted with a clean, minimal aesthetic, it features a regular fit with a relaxed waistline that offers comfort without compromising structure. The cropped length adds a modern edge, making it easy to style across casual and elevated looks. Made from combed and bio-washed cotton, this tee delivers a soft hand feel, breathability, and long-lasting durability. A versatile essential built for comfort, balance, and timeless appeal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality. Tumble dry on low 